# Install R packages if not installed -------------------------------------

if (!require(shiny)) install.packages("shiny")
if (!require(bs4Dash)) install.packages("bs4Dash")

library(shiny)
library(bs4Dash)


#Input
Sem<-"Fall Semester"
Year1<- "2024/2025"
data_optional<-c("O"="Optional course unit as a subject are not allowed to do this course unit.","C*"="Those who are doing Computer Science/ Information and Communication Technology/ Electronics and Embedded Systems are not allowed to do this course Unit","O#"="Optinal")
data_venue<-c("S1"="Science Auditorium", "P1"="Physics Lecture Theatre I", "C1"="Chemistry Lecture Theatre I","NFC4"=" New Faculty Complex (Third Floor)","SLR"="Specail Research Laboratory ","MCL1"="Mathematics Computer Lab 1","MCL2"="Mathematics Computer Lab 2","M1"="Mathematics Lecture Theatre 1","M2"="Mathematics Lecture Theatre 2","P1"="Physics Lecture Theatre 1")


# Data Pepration
Original_data<-data.frame(read.csv("Book2.csv"))

## Table Data 1
dataMon <-subset(Original_data,Original_data$Day=="Monday")[c(1,3,4,5,7)]
Original_dataue <-subset(Original_data,Original_data$Day=="Tuesday")[c(5,7)]
dataWed <-subset(Original_data,Original_data$Day=="Wednesday")[c(5,7)]
Original_datahu <-subset(Original_data,Original_data$Day=="Thursday")[c(5,7)]
dataFri <-subset(Original_data,Original_data$Day=="Friday")[c(5,7)]
dataMon$merge <-ifelse(dataMon$Course.Code != "", paste(dataMon$Course.Code, "(", dataMon$Hall, ")", sep = ""), "")
dataMon<-dataMon[-c(4,5)]
Original_dataue <- ifelse(Original_dataue$Course.Code != "", paste(Original_dataue$Course.Code, "(", Original_dataue$Hall, ")", sep = ""), "")
dataWed <- ifelse(dataWed$Course.Code != "", paste(dataWed$Course.Code, "(", dataWed$Hall, ")", sep = ""), "")
Original_datahu <- ifelse(Original_datahu$Course.Code != "", paste(Original_datahu$Course.Code, "(", Original_datahu$Hall, ")", sep = ""), "")
dataFri <- ifelse(dataFri$Course.Code != "", paste(dataFri$Course.Code, "(", dataFri$Hall, ")", sep = ""), "")


df<-data.frame(dataMon,Original_dataue,dataWed,Original_datahu,dataFri)
colnames(df)<-c("Year","Time","Subject","Monday","Tuesaday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday")

## Table 2 Data
data2<-(subset(Original_data,Original_data$Year==1)[c(4,5,6)])
data2 <- data2[!apply(is.na(data2) | data2 == "", 1, all),]

## Table 3
Time<-(c("08.00 - 08.50","08.55 - 09.45","09.45 - 10.15","10.15 - 11.05","11.10 - 12.00","12.00 - 01.00","01.00 - 02.00","02.00 - 03.00","03.00 - 04.00","04.00 - 05.00","05.00 - 05.45"))
Days<-c("Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday")

## Table 4

data3<-Original_data[8]
data3 <- data3[!apply(is.na(data3) | data3 == "", 1, all),]
data3
ls<-unique(data3)


# APPLICATION------------------------------------------------------------

ui <- dashboardPage(
  title= "Timetable Mangemnet App",
  header = dashboardHeader(
#    title = dashboardBrand(
#      title = " a",
#     color = "primary"
#      ),
    skin = "light",
    status = "blue",
    h3(strong("Departmental Timetable Organizer"))
  ),
  sidebar = dashboardSidebar(
    skin = "light",
    status = "primary",
    elevation = 3,
    width=500,
      sidebarUserPanel(
        image = 'logo.png',
        name = "ABC  Department"
      ),
    
      sidebarMenu(
        #sidebarHeader("Choose"),
        menuItem(
          "Master Timetable",
          tabName = "item1",
          icon = icon("calendar-alt")
        ),
        menuItem(
          "Hall Timetable",
          tabName = "item2",
          icon = icon("building")
        ),
        menuItem(
          "Lecturer Timetables",
          tabName = "item3",
          icon = icon("chalkboard-teacher")
        )
      )
  ),
      footer = dashboardFooter(
        left = p("Design by Ashan Jayamal"),
        right= p("Last updated: ", Sys.Date())
      ),
  body = dashboardBody(
    tabItems(
      tabItem(
        tabName = "item1",
        div(tags$img(src='logo.png', width='100px',height='100px'),style="text-align:center;"),
        titlePanel(title = h1(strong(paste("Timetable - ",Sem)), align = "center")),
        titlePanel(title = h2(strong(Year1), align = "center")),
        titlePanel(title = h3("Department of XYZ", align = "center")),
        titlePanel(title = h3("ABC University", align = "center")),
        fluidRow(
          selectInput(inputId = "YearInput",
            label="Choose a year",
            list("First Year","Second Year","Third Year (General)","Speical Part I","Speical Part II", "Extended Degree")
          ),
          selectInput(inputId = "SubjectInput",
                      label="Choose a Subject",
                      list("Mathematics","Applied Mathemtics","Manegemnet Scince")
          )
        ),fluidRow(column(12,
        tableOutput('table1'),align="center"),align="center"),
        p(strong("Course Titles, Lecturers in Charge and Venues")),
        tableOutput('table2'),
        htmlOutput('text7')
      ),
      tabItem(
        tabName = "item2",
        div(tags$img(src='logo.png', width='100px',height='100px'),style="text-align:center;"),
        titlePanel(title = h1(strong(paste("Timetable - ",Sem)), align = "center")),
        titlePanel(title = h2(strong(Year1), align = "center")),
        titlePanel(title = h3("Department of ABC", align = "center")),
        fluidRow(
          selectInput(inputId = "HallInput",
                      label="Choose the Hall",
                      list("M1","M2","SLR","MCL-1","MCL-2"),
          )
        ),
        fluidRow(column(12,
        tableOutput('table3'),align="center"),align="center"),
        tableOutput('table4')
      ),
     tabItem(
        tabName = "item3",
        div(tags$img(src='logo.png', width='100px',height='100px'),style="text-align:center;"),
        titlePanel(title = h1(strong(paste("Timetable - ",Sem)), align = "center")),
        titlePanel(title = h2(strong(Year1), align = "center")),
        titlePanel(title = h3("Department of ABC", align = "center")),
        fluidRow(
          selectInput(inputId = "LecturerInput",
                      label="Choose a  Name of Lecturer",
                      ls)
        ),fluidRow(column(12,
        tableOutput('table5'),align="center"),align="center"),
        tableOutput('table6')
        )
      )
    )
  )




# SERVER-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
server <- function(input, output,session) {
  output$table1 <-  renderTable({
    YearFilter<-subset(df,df$Year==input$YearInput & df$Subject==input$SubjectInput)[-c(1,3)]},
    na=" ",
    bordered = TRUE,
    hover = TRUE
    )
  output$table2 <-renderTable({
    data2<-(subset(Original_data,Original_data$Year==input$YearInput & Original_data$Subject==input$SubjectInput)[c(5,6,7,8)])
    data2<- unique(data2[!apply(is.na(data2) | data2 == "", 1, all),])
    data2<-data2[order(data2$Course.Code),]
    data2<-data2[data2$Course.Code!="Tutorials",]
    # Replace hall short names with full names
    data2$Hall <- sapply(data2$Hall, function(x) ifelse(x %in% names(data_venue), paste0(data_venue[x], " (", x, ")"), x))
    data2
    },   na=" "
  )
  output$table3<-renderTable({
   dataM1<-subset(Original_data,Original_data$Hall==input$HallInput)
#    list1<-match(dataM1[3][,1],Time)
#    list2<-match(dataM1[2][,1],Days)
    

    newdf <- data.frame(Time = Time, Monday = "", Tuesday = "", Wednesday = "", Thursday = "", Friday = "", stringsAsFactors = FALSE)
    for (i in 1:nrow(dataM1)) {
      row <- dataM1[i, ]
      time_index <- which(newdf$Time == row$Time)
      day_column <- which(names(newdf) == row$Day)
      if (newdf[time_index, day_column] == "") {
        newdf[time_index, day_column] <- row$Course.Code
      } else {
        newdf[time_index, day_column] <- paste(newdf[time_index, day_column], row$Course.Code, sep = "/")
      }
    }
    newdf
  },na=" ",border=TRUE,hover=TRUE)
  
  
  output$table4<-renderTable({
    dataM1<-unique((subset(Original_data,Original_data$Hall==input$HallInput))[c(5,6,8)])
  })
  
  
  output$table5<-renderTable({
    dataLec<-(subset(Original_data,Original_data$Lecturer==input$LecturerInput))
    listL1<-match(dataLec[3][,1],Time)
    listL2<-match(dataLec[2][,1],Days)
    newdfL = data.frame(matrix( 
      vector(), 11, 5, dimnames=list(c(), c("Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday"))), 
      stringsAsFactors=F)
    for (i in 1:length(listL1)){
      newdfL[listL1[i],listL2[i]]=dataLec[i,5]
    }
    newdfL<-data.frame(Time,newdfL)
  },na=" ",border=TRUE)
  
  
  
  output$table6<-renderTable({
    d<-unique((subset(Original_data,Original_data$Lecturer==input$LecturerInput))[c(5,6,7)])
    d$Hall <- sapply(d$Hall, function(x) ifelse(x %in% names(data_venue), paste0(data_venue[x], " (", x, ")"), x))
    d
  })
  
  output$text7<-renderUI({
    data7<-(subset(Original_data,Original_data$Year==input$YearInput & Original_data$Subject==input$SubjectInput)[c(9)])
    data7<- unique(data7[!apply(is.na(data7) | data7 == "", 1, all),])
    if(length(data7)!=0){
      lapply(data7, function(notation) {
        tags$div(paste(notation, "-", data_optional[notation]))
      })
    }
  })
}

shinyApp(ui = ui, server = server)
